28
00:02:01,720 --> 00:02:05,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That should do it 
for the midterm questions.</font>

29
00:02:06,050 --> 00:02:08,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This should help my students 
when they enter human society,</font>

30
00:02:08,820 --> 00:02:11,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I'll need to keep 
updating this material.</font>

31
00:02:13,350 --> 00:02:15,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Hoshino's stuff again?</font>

32
00:02:15,360 --> 00:02:17,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wish he'd keep his desk more organized.</font>

33
00:02:19,370 --> 00:02:22,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How does he keep track 
of where anything is?</font>

34
00:02:25,220 --> 00:02:27,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, I'm hungry.</font>

35
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:31,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With all this work, 
I had no time to eat lunch.</font>

36
00:02:31,210 --> 00:02:32,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, no!</font>

37
00:02:32,340 --> 00:02:34,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I forgot I bought sushi for lunch today!</font>

38
00:02:34,380 --> 00:02:35,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wasshoi!</i></font>

39
00:02:36,590 --> 00:02:38,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sushi, sushi!</font>

40
00:02:38,890 --> 00:02:42,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've gotta treat yourself sometimes.</font>

41
00:02:42,310 --> 00:02:47,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since I just got my paycheck, 
I splurged a bit with the premium sushi!</font>

42
00:02:48,780 --> 00:02:50,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? I can't open it.</font>

43
00:02:50,730 --> 00:02:52,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You <i>can't</i> be serious.</font>

44
00:02:52,430 --> 00:02:53,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, c'mon!</font>

45
00:02:53,740 --> 00:02:56,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There!</font>

46
00:02:58,680 --> 00:03:01,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aw man, I spilled it.</font>

47
00:03:02,610 --> 00:03:07,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is why I don't trust 
these tear-anywhere packets.</font>

48
00:03:09,110 --> 00:03:11,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There, all clean.</font>

49
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:12,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, huh?</font>

50
00:03:16,860 --> 00:03:19,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this Mr. Hoshino's handkerchief?!</font>

51
00:03:24,720 --> 00:03:26,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<b><font color="#7b8184"><font size="30">Advanced Class</font></font></b></font>

52
00:03:27,060 --> 00:03:28,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nope, it's not coming off.</font>

53
00:03:30,380 --> 00:03:32,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm a goner for sure!</font>

54
00:03:33,410 --> 00:03:34,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This sucks.</font>

55
00:03:34,940 --> 00:03:36,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What have I done?</font>

56
00:03:37,480 --> 00:03:39,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Hitoma, what's up?</font>

57
00:03:41,330 --> 00:03:42,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Haneda?!</font>

58
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:45,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What are <i>you</i> doing here so late?!</font>

59
00:03:45,070 --> 00:03:48,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, what'd you just hide from me?</font>

60
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:49,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

61
00:03:50,870 --> 00:03:53,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah! There's an alien up in the sky!</font>

62
00:03:53,580 --> 00:03:56,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Who would fall for that trick?</font>

63
00:03:58,030 --> 00:04:00,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wasn't trying to trick you...</font>

64
00:04:00,660 --> 00:04:02,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I saw everything.</font>

65
00:04:03,160 --> 00:04:04,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you talking about?</font>

66
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:08,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The fancy-looking handkerchief 
with that awful stain.</font>

67
00:04:08,420 --> 00:04:10,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you really <i>did</i> see?!</font>

68
00:04:10,170 --> 00:04:11,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">F-From where?</font>

69
00:04:11,450 --> 00:04:17,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">From "There, all done! That should do it 
for the midterm questions."</font>

70
00:04:17,170 --> 00:04:18,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All the way back then?!</font>

71
00:04:19,850 --> 00:04:22,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I might have messed up a little.</font>

72
00:04:22,320 --> 00:04:25,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't that Mr. Hoshino's?</font>

73
00:04:25,480 --> 00:04:26,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I knew it.</font>

74
00:04:26,950 --> 00:04:30,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should apologize 
to him sooner rather than later.</font>

75
00:04:30,660 --> 00:04:36,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I agree, but I wanted to do what I could 
before returning it to him.</font>

76
00:04:36,650 --> 00:04:39,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't think you'll get anywhere 
by stressing yourself out.</font>

77
00:04:39,750 --> 00:04:41,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah...</font>

78
00:04:41,790 --> 00:04:44,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll go get Mr. Hoshino, then.</font>

79
00:04:44,890 --> 00:04:46,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, Haneda!</font>

80
00:04:46,130 --> 00:04:48,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need time to sort out my emotions!</font>

81
00:04:49,090 --> 00:04:50,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here he is.</font>

82
00:04:50,530 --> 00:04:51,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was fast!</font>

83
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:53,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd already asked him to come here.</font>

84
00:04:53,110 --> 00:04:54,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now <i>that's</i> being prepared!</font>

85
00:04:54,520 --> 00:04:55,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh, what?</font>

86
00:04:55,600 --> 00:04:56,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's this about?</font>

87
00:04:56,690 --> 00:04:58,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, Mr. Hoshino...</font>

88
00:04:59,620 --> 00:05:01,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You see...</font>

89
00:05:01,590 --> 00:05:06,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that's the handkerchief I got 
as a birthday present from my wife.</font>

90
00:05:06,330 --> 00:05:08,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Y-Your wife?!</font>

91
00:05:08,180 --> 00:05:10,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As a birthday present?!</font>

92
00:05:10,840 --> 00:05:13,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hold on, you're married?!</font>

93
00:05:13,570 --> 00:05:17,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was stumped since I couldn't find it.</font>

94
00:05:17,290 --> 00:05:18,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

95
00:05:18,770 --> 00:05:19,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where was it?</font>

96
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:26,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think it turned up when 
that pile of paper on your desk collapsed.</font>

97
00:05:26,390 --> 00:05:29,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, so that's where it was?</font>

98
00:05:29,130 --> 00:05:30,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry for all the trouble.</font>

99
00:05:30,750 --> 00:05:33,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've never been very organized.</font>

100
00:05:33,540 --> 00:05:36,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, Mr. Hoshino.</font>

101
00:05:37,080 --> 00:05:40,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, I used this to wipe 
up some soy sauce by mistake.</font>

102
00:05:40,990 --> 00:05:42,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so sorry!</font>

103
00:05:42,700 --> 00:05:43,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Soy sauce?</font>

104
00:05:46,630 --> 00:05:49,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, a stain like that's no big deal.</font>

105
00:05:49,700 --> 00:05:52,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's still perfectly usable 
as a handkerchief.</font>

106
00:05:52,380 --> 00:05:54,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't need to feel bad about it 
at all, Mr. Hitoma.</font>

107
00:05:54,870 --> 00:05:57,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so glad you managed to find it.</font>

108
00:05:57,710 --> 00:06:00,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was looking for it over the past week.</font>

109
00:06:00,230 --> 00:06:02,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My wife was about to be very angry at me.</font>

110
00:06:02,540 --> 00:06:06,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss Haneda, is this 
why you called me here?</font>

111
00:06:06,260 --> 00:06:07,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right.</font>

112
00:06:07,470 --> 00:06:08,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

113
00:06:08,660 --> 00:06:11,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss Haneda. Mr. Hitoma. Thank you both.</font>

114
00:06:11,790 --> 00:06:12,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not at all.</font>

115
00:06:13,180 --> 00:06:14,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be going now.</font>

116
00:06:18,610 --> 00:06:21,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad he didn't get mad at you.</font>

117
00:06:21,380 --> 00:06:22,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

118
00:06:22,430 --> 00:06:23,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks a lot, Haneda.</font>

119
00:06:23,980 --> 00:06:26,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Guess I'll be going, too!</font>

120
00:06:29,270 --> 00:06:30,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Tobari Haneda.</i></font>

121
00:06:31,160 --> 00:06:33,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Her true form is a bird, 
the bull-headed shrike.</i></font>

122
00:06:33,460 --> 00:06:35,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She's always been top of the class.</i></font>

123
00:06:35,670 --> 00:06:38,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>However, her school records 
are sealed away for some reason,</i></font>

124
00:06:38,920 --> 00:06:41,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>so I don't know how long 
she's spent at the advanced level.</i></font>

125
00:06:42,040 --> 00:06:45,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She wants to become 
a human so she can make music.</i></font>

126
00:06:49,300 --> 00:06:51,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<b><font color="#7b8184"><font size="30">Advanced Class</font></font></b></font>

127
00:06:54,170 --> 00:06:55,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Hitoma.</font>

128
00:06:56,500 --> 00:06:57,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it, Haneda?</font>

129
00:06:58,110 --> 00:07:00,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My stomach hurts a little.</font>

130
00:07:00,800 --> 00:07:02,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">May I go to the nurse's office?</font>

131
00:07:02,890 --> 00:07:05,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. Who's willing to tag along?</font>

132
00:07:05,070 --> 00:07:06,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I'll be fine.</font>

133
00:07:06,770 --> 00:07:08,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can make it there by myself.</font>

134
00:07:09,330 --> 00:07:11,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, we can't have you 
passing out in the hallway.</font>

135
00:07:11,830 --> 00:07:13,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can one of you please take her?</font>

136
00:07:13,550 --> 00:07:14,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll do it!</font>

137
00:07:15,310 --> 00:07:16,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure, Usami.</font>

138
00:07:16,750 --> 00:07:18,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please accompany her.</font>

139
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:19,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Got it.</font>

140
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:22,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I'm really fine by myself.</font>

141
00:07:22,670 --> 00:07:24,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't look it, so shut your trap.</font>

142
00:07:25,130 --> 00:07:28,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? This isn't the Usami I know.</font>

143
00:07:28,850 --> 00:07:31,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't classes come first?</font>

144
00:07:31,050 --> 00:07:33,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You sure can run your mouth 
for someone who's sick.</font>

145
00:07:33,760 --> 00:07:35,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hurry up and rest in the nurse's office.</font>

146
00:07:44,460 --> 00:07:47,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will Tobari be all right?</font>

147
00:07:47,540 --> 00:07:53,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We rarely even catch colds in this form, 
so I can't help but worry.</font>

148
00:07:53,110 --> 00:07:55,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh, really?</font>

149
00:07:55,050 --> 00:08:00,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our current bodies are that 
of a model healthy human teenager.</font>

150
00:08:00,030 --> 00:08:04,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We enjoy full bodily function, 
which includes fitness and immune systems.</font>

151
00:08:04,900 --> 00:08:07,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In turn, we don't get sick very easily.</font>

152
00:08:07,290 --> 00:08:10,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<b><font color="#656c6f"><font size="24">Nurse's Office</font></font></b></font>

153
00:08:09,240 --> 00:08:10,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, come in.</font>

154
00:08:10,930 --> 00:08:12,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me.</font>

155
00:08:12,380 --> 00:08:14,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">'Sup, Mr. Hitoma.</font>

156
00:08:14,860 --> 00:08:16,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doing good?</font>

157
00:08:16,050 --> 00:08:18,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello there, Ms. Karasuma.</font>

158
00:08:18,950 --> 00:08:21,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How's Haneda doing?</font>

159
00:08:21,060 --> 00:08:24,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Feeling a lot better after a nap.</font>

160
00:08:24,440 --> 00:08:26,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see, that's good to hear.</font>

161
00:08:26,700 --> 00:08:29,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Hitoma, you should have 
a talk with her, too.</font>

162
00:08:30,840 --> 00:08:35,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tobari Haneda always comes to the 
nurse's office at the very last minute.</font>

163
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:36,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Always?</font>

164
00:08:36,870 --> 00:08:42,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She gets sick at this time every year, 
so tell her to drop by a little earlier.</font>

165
00:08:42,180 --> 00:08:44,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And to get some proper rest, too.</font>

166
00:08:44,430 --> 00:08:46,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Every year?</font>

167
00:08:46,350 --> 00:08:48,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Does she have some kind of condition?</font>

168
00:08:48,660 --> 00:08:49,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Oops.</font>

169
00:08:49,670 --> 00:08:52,710
