00:09:16,470 --> 00:09:18,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The least he could do is share!</font>

179
00:09:19,950 --> 00:09:23,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I haven't had a chance to talk 
