203
00:10:18,880 --> 00:10:19,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Uh-oh.</i></font>

204
00:10:19,850 --> 00:10:22,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I need to do something 
to keep my alter ego under wraps!</i></font>

205
00:10:22,180 --> 00:10:25,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-Haneda, have you ever tried 
to make your own music?</font>

206
00:10:27,490 --> 00:10:29,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've messed around 
with making music here and there.</font>

207
00:10:29,700 --> 00:10:32,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just like Mr. Hitoman.</font>

208
00:10:32,020 --> 00:10:33,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

209
00:10:33,320 --> 00:10:34,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey...</font>

210
00:10:34,940 --> 00:10:39,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you feel all better now, 
I'd prefer it if you booked it outta here.</font>

211
00:10:39,740 --> 00:10:42,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, sure...</font>

212
00:10:42,700 --> 00:10:44,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<b><font color="#656c6f"><font size="24">Nurse's Office</font></font></b></font>

213
00:10:47,110 --> 00:10:48,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll be fine heading home?</font>

214
00:10:48,540 --> 00:10:51,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I'm all good now!</font>

215
00:10:55,110 --> 00:10:58,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not very considerate though, are you?</font>

216
00:10:58,320 --> 00:10:59,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why not?</font>

217
00:10:59,340 --> 00:11:03,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At times like these, wouldn't you usually 
bring my stuff to the nurse's office?</font>

218
00:11:03,820 --> 00:11:08,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You think I'm brave enough 
to touch my female students' belongings?</font>

219
00:11:08,050 --> 00:11:09,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess you're right.</font>

220
00:11:09,370 --> 00:11:12,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One wrong move, and it could 
be considered sexual harassment.</font>

221
00:11:12,030 --> 00:11:13,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right?</font>

222
00:11:13,170 --> 00:11:14,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've thought all this through.</font>

223
00:11:16,140 --> 00:11:19,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Well, it's true that
I was being inconsiderate.</i></font>

224
00:11:21,060 --> 00:11:21,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's right.</i></font>

225
00:11:22,150 --> 00:11:23,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Nothing good ever comes from meddling.</i></font>

226
00:11:26,990 --> 00:11:28,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<b><font color="#a56d57"><font size="30"><font size="22">Advanced Class</font></font></font></b></font>

227
00:11:31,000 --> 00:11:33,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wish I could go home, too.</font>

228
00:11:33,350 --> 00:11:36,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're really gonna say 
that in front of a student?</font>

229
00:11:36,380 --> 00:11:39,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong with being honest 
when you want to go home?</font>

230
00:11:39,860 --> 00:11:43,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've still got lots 
of work I need to get done.</font>

231
00:11:43,800 --> 00:11:45,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Must be nice being able to leave.</font>

232
00:11:45,870 --> 00:11:48,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not like you can 
just ignore your work.</font>

233
00:11:48,080 --> 00:11:50,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, work hard, but too hard.</font>

234
00:11:50,870 --> 00:11:51,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure.</font>

235
00:11:51,610 --> 00:11:53,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't work yourself too hard, either.</font>

236
00:11:53,740 --> 00:11:56,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know you were helping 
Usami study the other day.</font>

237
00:11:56,400 --> 00:11:57,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How do you know that?!</font>

238
00:11:58,690 --> 00:12:00,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can tell as your teacher.</font>

239
00:12:01,160 --> 00:12:02,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I spoke with the other teachers.</font>

240
00:12:03,390 --> 00:12:07,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Usami's been getting better 
grades on her quizzes overall.</font>

241
00:12:07,300 --> 00:12:11,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't help but cheer 
on someone who's trying so hard.</font>

242
00:12:12,080 --> 00:12:15,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You really keep an eye on us, though, huh?</font>

243
00:12:16,210 --> 00:12:17,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pretty much.</font>

244
00:12:17,190 --> 00:12:19,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's my job as a teacher.</font>

245
00:12:21,070 --> 00:12:25,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been keeping 
a good eye on you as well.</font>

246
00:12:26,540 --> 00:12:27,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's true.</i></font>

247
00:12:27,720 --> 00:12:30,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She knew about how I got 
Mr. Hoshino's handkerchief dirty,</i></font>

248
00:12:30,830 --> 00:12:33,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and how I make MADs to upload online.</i></font>

249
00:12:34,500 --> 00:12:35,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Hitoma.</font>

250
00:12:36,770 --> 00:12:41,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're usually easygoing and careless, 
but you can look real sad sometimes.</font>

251
00:12:41,510 --> 00:12:42,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

252
00:12:42,460 --> 00:12:44,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With a faraway look in your eyes.</font>

253
00:12:45,220 --> 00:12:46,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?</font>

254
00:12:46,390 --> 00:12:47,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

255
00:12:47,360 --> 00:12:51,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like when I said you 
were inconsiderate back in the hallway.</font>

256
00:12:53,950 --> 00:12:57,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, did I touch a sore spot?</font>

257
00:12:58,450 --> 00:13:00,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, that's not it.</font>

258
00:13:00,730 --> 00:13:03,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I did, I'm sorry.</font>

259
00:13:05,430 --> 00:13:07,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, it really <i>was</i> that?</font>

260
00:13:12,210 --> 00:13:16,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If something's bothering you, 
I'm here to listen.</font>

261
00:13:16,290 --> 00:13:21,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or well, if you tell me, 
then I can avoid it in the future.</font>

262
00:13:22,570 --> 00:13:23,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, it's fine.</font>

263
00:13:24,600 --> 00:13:26,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry to bother you like that.</font>

264
00:13:27,720 --> 00:13:30,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Besides, it's all in the past.</font>

265
00:13:31,260 --> 00:13:36,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You still think about it 
because you can't leave it in the past.</font>

266
00:13:36,630 --> 00:13:38,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Am I wrong when I say that?</font>

267
00:13:42,180 --> 00:13:45,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Talking about it might 
be a weight off your mind.</font>

268
00:13:47,370 --> 00:13:49,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There you go, looking sad again.</font>

269
00:13:50,310 --> 00:13:51,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, sorry.</font>

270
00:13:52,040 --> 00:13:53,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's all right.</font>

271
00:13:54,460 --> 00:13:57,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter what, you always have me here.</font>

272
00:13:59,130 --> 00:14:02,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it okay to stop bearing this weight?</font>

273
00:14:03,810 --> 00:14:05,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why not?</font>

274
00:14:05,450 --> 00:14:09,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think that's how it becomes 
a thing of the past.</font>

275
00:14:11,740 --> 00:14:13,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To tell the truth...</font>

276
00:14:13,530 --> 00:14:14,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah?</font>

277
00:14:15,790 --> 00:14:19,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At my old school, one of my 
students asked me for help.</font>

278
00:14:20,670 --> 00:14:22,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She was fighting with a friend of hers.</font>

279
00:14:23,660 --> 00:14:26,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As her homeroom teacher, 
I wanted to do what I could.</font>

280
00:14:27,660 --> 00:14:28,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

281
00:14:30,330 --> 00:14:31,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But that was a mistake.</font>

282
00:14:32,600 --> 00:14:34,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In the end, because of me...</font>

283
00:14:34,410 --> 00:14:39,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because I stepped in, 
things got even more out of hand.</font>

284
00:14:40,170 --> 00:14:43,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That student ended up
leaving school altogether.</font>

285
00:14:45,670 --> 00:14:49,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And then, right before she did,</font>

286
00:14:49,410 --> 00:14:52,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">she said I physically punished her, 
even though I never laid a finger.</font>

287
00:14:54,730 --> 00:14:57,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The administration wouldn't listen 
to a word I said on the matter.</font>

288
00:14:59,130 --> 00:15:02,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which is why I ended up 
having to leave as well.</font>

289
00:15:05,940 --> 00:15:10,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">On my last day, that student 
came up to me and said...</font>

290
00:15:11,110 --> 00:15:13,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is all your fault!</font>

291
00:15:15,900 --> 00:15:17,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And she was right.</font>

292
00:15:17,890 --> 00:15:19,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was in the wrong.</font>

293
00:15:19,820 --> 00:15:20,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why...</font>

294
00:15:21,580 --> 00:15:22,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Hitoma.</font>

295
00:15:23,180 --> 00:15:25,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Time doesn't stand still.</font>

296
00:15:25,620 --> 00:15:26,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

297
00:15:27,550 --> 00:15:31,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your past self may never leave you,</font>

298
00:15:31,570 --> 00:15:34,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but the present you is the one I see now.</font>

299
00:15:35,540 --> 00:15:38,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You may make mistakes, 
but you can always start over.</font>

300
00:15:39,210 --> 00:15:40,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry.</font>

301
00:15:40,340 --> 00:15:44,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm right here, seeing you as you are now.</font>

302
00:15:51,490 --> 00:15:52,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

303
00:15:52,550 --> 00:15:54,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I could say the same.</font>

304
00:15:54,330 --> 00:15:57,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for coming to this school.</font>

305
00:15:57,970 --> 00:15:58,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

306
00:15:59,100 --> 00:16:00,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Hitoma.</font>

307
00:16:00,730 --> 00:16:02,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You said you want to leave for the day?</font>

308
00:16:09,990 --> 00:16:12,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">M-Miss Haneda?</font>

309
00:16:13,620 --> 00:16:14,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Hitoma.</font>

310
00:16:15,290 --> 00:16:19,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How about the two 
of us run away somewhere?</font>

311
00:16:24,150 --> 00:16:27,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are we allowed to be up here?</font>

312
00:16:27,710 --> 00:16:30,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And wait, they don't lock 
the door to the rooftop?</font>

313
00:16:31,100 --> 00:16:33,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Usually, they do.</font>

314
00:16:33,020 --> 00:16:35,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Regular students 
are prohibited from entering.</font>

315
00:16:35,300 --> 00:16:37,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you're breaking school rules?!</font>

316
00:16:37,010 --> 00:16:39,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then how come it was unlocked?</font>

317
00:16:40,590 --> 00:16:43,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's easy to get up here 
if you use this to pick the lock.</font>

318
00:16:43,400 --> 00:16:44,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know you shouldn't do that!</font>

319
00:16:46,580 --> 00:16:48,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doesn't it feel good 
up here on the rooftop?</font>

320
00:16:49,170 --> 00:16:51,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I come up here all the time.</font>

321
00:16:55,560 --> 00:16:56,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well?</font>

322
00:16:56,670 --> 00:16:58,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did this clear your head a little?</font>

323
00:16:58,800 --> 00:16:59,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

324
00:16:59,620 --> 00:17:02,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, maybe it did.</font>

325
00:17:02,580 --> 00:17:04,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're so funny.</font>

326
00:17:05,130 --> 00:17:06,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Haneda.</font>

327
00:17:06,120 --> 00:17:10,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, but you're losing points for 
sneaking onto the roof against regulation.</font>

328
00:17:11,030 --> 00:17:12,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I don't mind.</font>

329
00:17:12,640 --> 00:17:15,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then since I'm losing points 
anyway, how about this?</font>

330
00:17:17,090 --> 00:17:19,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Hitoma, turn around for me.</font>

331
00:17:19,660 --> 00:17:21,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">T-Turn around?</font>

332
00:17:21,040 --> 00:17:22,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just trust me!</font>

333
00:17:28,270 --> 00:17:30,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is this what I think it is?!</i></font>

334
00:17:30,830 --> 00:17:34,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Aren't you coming 
on a little too strong, Miss Haneda?!</i></font>

335
00:17:35,330 --> 00:17:37,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So it's true that they feel soft!</i></font>

336
00:17:37,590 --> 00:17:38,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wait no, I shouldn't be enjoying this!</i></font>

337
00:17:40,540 --> 00:17:44,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm starting to feel lightheaded now.</i></font>

338
00:17:44,040 --> 00:17:46,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Like my body is floating in midair...</i></font>

339
00:17:46,650 --> 00:17:47,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wait...</i></font>

340
00:17:51,140 --> 00:17:53,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">M-M-Miss Haneda, we're floating!</font>

341
00:17:53,660 --> 00:17:55,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure, since we're flying.</font>

342
00:17:55,650 --> 00:17:58,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can deduct points 
for unhuman-like behavior!</font>

343
00:17:58,610 --> 00:18:00,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Keep squirming and you'll fall.</font>

344
00:18:01,260 --> 00:18:02,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry.</font>

345
00:18:02,710 --> 00:18:05,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just act normal and I won't drop you.</font>

346
00:18:05,180 --> 00:18:07,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know how scary this is?!</font>

347
00:18:07,090 --> 00:18:09,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My safety instinct is sounding its alarms!</font>

348
00:18:09,720 --> 00:18:11,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a weird way to put it.</font>

349
00:18:11,610 --> 00:18:15,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case, put your 
arms around my neck.</font>

350
00:18:15,310 --> 00:18:15,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

351
00:18:17,300 --> 00:18:19,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Feel a little better now?</font>

352
00:18:19,520 --> 00:18:22,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I do feel safer...</font>

353
00:18:23,460 --> 00:18:26,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Although it has me nervous in another way.</i></font>

354
00:18:26,160 --> 00:18:28,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, are you thinking something dirty?</font>

355
00:18:28,710 --> 00:18:30,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, not at all.</font>

356
00:18:30,490 --> 00:18:31,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good.</font>

357
00:18:31,500 --> 00:18:33,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go on, take a look.</font>

358
00:18:41,180 --> 00:18:43,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When you see the sky from up above,</font>

359
00:18:43,980 --> 00:18:46,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it looks so much bigger 
and more beautiful than from below.</font>

360
00:18:47,150 --> 00:18:50,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanted to show you what it looks like.</font>

361
00:18:52,710 --> 00:18:53,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Hitoma.</font>

362
00:18:53,800 --> 00:18:59,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to be like this sky, 
and accept you for everything you are.</font>

363
00:19:00,030 --> 00:19:01,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you confessing to me?</font>

364
00:19:01,530 --> 00:19:03,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't get too full of yourself.</font>

365
00:19:04,230 --> 00:19:05,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry...</font>

366
00:19:11,170 --> 00:19:12,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

367
00:19:13,300 --> 00:19:15,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you have fun, Mr. Hitoma?</font>

368
00:19:15,870 --> 00:19:17,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I sure did.</font>

369
00:19:17,770 --> 00:19:21,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you broke way too many 
rules in front of a teacher.</font>

370
00:19:22,220 --> 00:19:24,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't blame me if you can't become human.</font>

371
00:19:25,420 --> 00:19:26,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's fine by me.</font>

372
00:19:26,960 --> 00:19:31,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In fact, it makes me happy 
to see you treat me fairly.</font>

373
00:19:31,190 --> 00:19:33,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you want to become human?</font>

374
00:19:33,530 --> 00:19:34,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I do.</font>

375
00:19:35,560 --> 00:19:40,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I don't have to just yet.</font>

376
00:19:40,900 --> 00:19:42,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What does that mean?</font>

377
00:19:44,010 --> 00:19:45,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a secret for now.</font>

378
00:19:47,230 --> 00:19:49,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What she did today will lose her points.</i></font>

379
00:19:50,360 --> 00:19:54,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>All for bringing me here to try 
and cheer me up.</i></font>

380
00:19:54,610 --> 00:19:56,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even so, I'm a teacher.</i></font>

381
00:19:57,510 --> 00:20:00,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Outside of academic exams, 
all I can do is take points away.</i></font>

382
00:20:01,420 --> 00:20:02,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Then why don't I...</i></font>

383
00:20:03,270 --> 00:20:04,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Haneda.</font>

384
00:20:05,850 --> 00:20:08,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You like music, don't you?</font>

385
00:20:08,580 --> 00:20:10,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, that's right.</font>

386
00:20:10,410 --> 00:20:12,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Both listening to music and singing.</font>

387
00:20:12,660 --> 00:20:16,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then can I ask you to sing 
for me right now?</font>

388
00:20:16,650 --> 00:20:18,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here?!</font>

389
00:20:18,080 --> 00:20:20,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You watched my MAD video 
in the nurse's office.</font>

390
00:20:20,540 --> 00:20:22,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Think of it as a fair trade.</font>

391
00:20:22,520 --> 00:20:23,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

392
00:20:23,690 --> 00:20:25,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Flying in the air doesn't count?</font>

393
00:20:25,620 --> 00:20:28,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was a flagrant 
rule violation, so nope.</font>

394
00:20:28,760 --> 00:20:31,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You said it was fun, too.</font>

395
00:20:31,510 --> 00:20:34,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, if you'd rather not, 
then that's fine.</font>

396
00:20:34,030 --> 00:20:35,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

397
00:20:41,720 --> 00:20:45,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you okay even if 
it doesn't sound very good?</font>

398
00:20:45,220 --> 00:20:46,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me hear it.</font>

399
00:20:48,940 --> 00:20:51,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just this once, then.</font>

